{
  "stem": "1550.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we were not allowed to go back to Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know I mean?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So what happened, we were stopped on the border.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were put into a room there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they made some jokes with us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had to crawl under the bed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some other people came, some nasty Nazis came.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They told me to crawl under the bed and start singing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then he said to me, OK, jump.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Start jumping.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had to jump, and then I had to do this and that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I wasn't beaten up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I must say, I wasn't beaten up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then I was sent back to-- so on the same day, I arrived back in Bratislava in the camp again, after my adventure with the-- with the German.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "After that, I said, I'll never go back to this bloody country again, you know after that experience.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So that was-- that was-- that was that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Now that was-- it must have been February or March of 1939.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we were still were stuck in this-- the Danube was by then, unfrozen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But they still were not able to arrange all the ships and everything and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Then it was summer of 1940.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then France was defeated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And-- and the Germans occupied practically the whole of Europe.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But that didn't affect us, actually.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then I got a letter one fine day from my parents that my parents told me that another transport is going to Palestine, another illegal transport from Vienna, which could-- which is probably in combination with mine.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they are going to join that one, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "By that time, it was late in the summer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I got the-- like I said, I got a postcard from my parents.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
